  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal profile)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. This assessment evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification is performed; all 13 credibility factors are assessed against MRL-5 requirements. The intended use is prediction of hemolysis index under VAD operating conditions (flow rates 2–6 L/min, rotational speeds 2000–4000 RPM) to support a 510(k) submission for a Class III implantable rotary blood pump. Decision: Accepted following remediation of identified gaps.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/vad-hemolysis-mrl5-req-001",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/cfd-hemolysis-vad-class3-claim-001",
  "bindsModel": "https://uofa.net/synth/model/cfd-hemolysis-centrifugal-pump-v3",
